name: FedEx A310-300F taxi at Edmonton Airport
description:
This is a video of a FedEx Airbus A310-300F taxiing past me at Edmonton International Airport (CYEG/YEG). Aircraft registration N813FD. Enjoy the video, and please comment, rate, and subscribe!
If you want to see a passenger version of this plane taking off, go to this video:
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Udt9m_2dgTY
